# Frontend (`apps/web`)

Per ADR-008:

- Next.js + TypeScript
- Business logic does NOT live in React components
- API client generated from OpenAPI where possible
- Graph visualization behind an adapter component
- Accessible design system based on headless primitives

## MVP surfaces

Sources/sync, processing status, proposal approval, hybrid search/Q&A, entity/graph views, audit, errors.

## Data fetching

Use `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` for API base. Handle API error envelope consistently.
